data.description: Better than new! This 2022 build boasts 4 generous bedrooms, 2.5 baths light and bright livening space w/10' ceilings, and so much more! Chefs will love this kitchen with tons of prep and serving space. Huge Pantry, dual ovens, cabinets w/crown, pendant lights above island, stainless appliances. Split floorplan w/primary on one side of home and additional rooms on the other. Primary w/en-suite bath, huge walk in closet. 5-panel doors throughout. Great room style floor plan is awesome for entertaining. Convenient to shopping, schools and recreation.
